<div class="sidenav">
  <div class="sidenav-text">
    <%= link_to dashboard_page_path do %>
      My Dashboard
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to networks_page_path do %>
      My Networks
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to suggested_roadmap_path do %>
      Create Roadmap
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="dashboard">
  <div class="dashboard-row">
    <div class="dashboard-card">
  <div class="cover-bg">
    <%= link_to edit_profile_path, class: 'btn btn-edit mr-4 mt-3' do %>
    Edit
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="user-info-wrap">
    <div class="user-photo"><%= @user.photo.attached? ? cl_image_path(@user.photo.key) : asset_path('placeholder.jpg') %></div>
    <div class="user-info">
      <div class="user-name"><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></div>
      <div class="user-title"><%= @user.current_role %> in <%= @user.current_industry %> @ <%= @user.location %> Singapore</div>
      <div class="user-title mt-0">Aiming to become a/an <%= @user.future_role %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="user-bio">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
      <h3 class="bio-subject">Budget</h3>SGD <%= @user.budget %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
      <h3 class="bio-subject">Timeframe</h3><%= @user.timeframe %> months 
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-12 pt-3">
      <h3 class="bio-subject">Motivation</h3><%= @user.motivation %>I'm a tech enthusiast and have been always curious to learn about how tech works.
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-12 pt-3">
      <h3 class="bio-subject">Journey Experience</h3><%= @user.journey_experience %>My journey from a product marketing manager to a fullstack software engineer was definitely not easy but worth all the efforts and time. Initially I tried some free courses on codecademy blabla.
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-12 pt-3">
      <h3 class="bio-subject">Advice/Tips To Share</h3><%= @user.advice %>I regret for not starting learning programming earlier, so if you are still debating, my advice is definitel GO AND TRY IT FIRST! It may sound daunting to switch your career and start something from scratch blabla.
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-12 pt-3">
      <h3 class="bio-subject">Satisfied To The New Role In Tech?</h3><%= @user.satisfaction %> 
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  </div>
</div> 